ws2d.init

Enum InitializationState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<InitializationState>
      • ws2d.init.InitializationState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<InitializationState>

    public enum InitializationState
extends java.lang.Enum<InitializationState>
    An initialization state: see the enumerated values for details.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BOOT
      The very first stage of initialization where the platform is just launching.
      FINISHED
      Marks the end of all initialization stages.
      INIT
      The initialization stage is where all game object are registered.
      POST_INIT
      The post-initialization stage is where more external connections can take place as well as any changes in on-disk data after initialization.
      PRE_INIT
      The pre-initialization stage is where loggers are finalized and where external server communications can take place.
